HEADWORD: Rocambole
<hw>Roc"am*bole</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>rokambole</asp>.]</altsp> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A name of <spn>Allium Scorodoprasum</spn> and <spn>Allium
Ascalonium</spn>, two kinds of garlic, the latter of which is also
called <altname>shallot</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

